// Company Law (views/law/company.pug)
extends ../layouts/main

block content
  .law-container
    .container
      h1 Company Law
      .law-section
        h2 Step 1: What is Company Law about?
        p Company law governs the formation, operation, and dissolution of companies. In India, it is primarily governed by the Companies Act, 2013, which replaced the Companies Act, 1956.
        p This area of law covers incorporation procedures, compliance requirements, corporate governance, mergers and acquisitions, winding up procedures, and the rights and duties of shareholders, directors, and other stakeholders.
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 2: Why do we need Company Law and Solutions?
        h3 Why We Need Company Law:
        ul
          li Protection of shareholder interests
          li Corporate governance and transparency
          li Standardized procedures for incorporation and compliance
          li Dispute resolution mechanisms
          li Regulation of capital markets and investor protection
        h3 Solutions:
        ul
          li Regular compliance with ROC filings
          li Proper corporate governance practices
          li Timely statutory audits and returns
          li Professional legal and compliance support
          li Use of technology for compliance management
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 3: Help and Description
        h3 Key Areas of Company Law:
        .company-areas
          .area-card
            h4 Incorporation
            p Procedures for forming private, public, and one-person companies
          .area-card
            h4 Compliance
            p Annual filings, board meetings, and statutory requirements
          .area-card
            h4 Corporate Governance
            p Director duties, shareholder rights, and board responsibilities
          .area-card
            h4 Mergers & Acquisitions
            p Procedures for business combinations and restructuring
          .area-card
            h4 Winding Up
            p Voluntary and compulsory dissolution procedures
        h3 Important Procedures:
        ul
          li Company incorporation through SPICe+ form
          li Director Identification Number (DIN) and Digital Signature Certificate (DSC)
          li ROC annual returns and compliance filings
          li Board and general meetings procedures
          li Financial statement and audit requirements
      
      .chatbot-section
        h2 Company Law Chatbot
        .chatbot-container
          .chat-messages#chat-messages
            .message.bot-message
              p Welcome! I can help you with company law queries. What would you like to know about incorporation, compliance, or corporate governance?
          .chat-input-container
            input(type='text', id='chat-input', placeholder='Ask about company law...', class='law-chat-input')
            button#send-btn Send